room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did the 0 Dark 30 room and we had an amazing time! It was challenging and fun all wrapped in one. Henry is a sweetie pie and a great game master!

room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did 0-Dark 30. Really fun, highly recommend going here!

room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Lots of fun but don't do the 0 dark thirty if you're a newbie... very challenging!

room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: So much fun! We did the 0 dark thirty room and it was challenging but awesome! Awesome staff too!

room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Went with a group of friends. There was 7 of us in total. We did the 0 Dark 30. We had a blast, and finished with 1 minute and 16 seconds left. We will be back again to do a different room.
